description	"Cin Drallig

^2Weaponry:
- Cin Drallig's Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red / Blue Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Gun Defense   (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (3)
- Push  (2)
- Sense (1)
- Speed (3)

^8Attributes:
- Agility (Faster Movement)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (1)

Cin Drallig (69 BBY - 19 BBY) was a Jedi Master in the years during and prior to the Clone Wars, and trained Anakin Skywalker in the advanced use of a lightsaber. He was a legendary lightsaber instructor at the Jedi Temple on Coruscant, and though he was not a member of the Jedi Council, his dueling abilities likely rivaled those of the Council members. His apprentice during this time was Serra Keto."